QAIL — Query as AST, Inject to Language
Copyright 2025 QAIL Contributors

This product includes software developed by the QAIL project
(https://qail.rs).

QAIL is an AST-native database protocol that encodes queries directly
to PostgreSQL wire format bytes — skipping SQL string generation,
preventing injection by construction, and enabling zero-copy execution.

For more information, visit:
  https://qail.rs        — Protocol documentation
  https://qail.io        — Managed QAIL platform
  https://github.com/qail-io/qail — Source code
